    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/4b77b2e411fe9fe8f0d6c912f40590bd.poster.avif?t=1739889080\" width=622 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/4b77b2e411fe9fe8f0d6c912f40590bd.webm?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/4b77b2e411fe9fe8f0d6c912f40590bd.mp4?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《The Shape Killer》，这是一款充满动感的卡通狙击游戏，您将扮演一名雇佣兵，执行消灭高调目标的任务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/68c187bc1d41b1e5f37bc84f65cedcb9.poster.avif?t=1739889080\" width=622 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/68c187bc1d41b1e5f37bc84f65cedcb9.webm?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/68c187bc1d41b1e5f37bc84f65cedcb9.mp4?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个游戏中，您需要使用所有技能来消灭目标，同时保持低调。使用您值得信赖的狙击步枪和敏锐的眼光，您需要在各种城市完成任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/a472e87c8056d1633190dcfd2237a995.poster.avif?t=1739889080\" width=622 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/a472e87c8056d1633190dcfd2237a995.webm?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/a472e87c8056d1633190dcfd2237a995.mp4?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Shape Killer》拥有令人惊叹的卡通图形和身临其境的游戏玩法，让您扮演职业杀手。使用您的技能追踪目标，找到完美的位置，一枪将他们击毙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/cfb776459a726117bfb671ef5c44a0bd.poster.avif?t=1739889080\" width=622 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/cfb776459a726117bfb671ef5c44a0bd.webm?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380940/extras/cfb776459a726117bfb671ef5c44a0bd.mp4?t=1739889080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名雇佣兵，您需要做出战略决策来完成任务并获得报酬。您会选择默默地消灭目标，还是会开枪射击？选择权在您手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您还在等什么？拿起步枪，接受合同，准备成为终极合同狙击手！</p>",
